{"tid":432453,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"FIFA 高手請進","createTime":"2017-10-11T14:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T15:49:07.000Z","uid":15939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f78d25fc16f0e4c8e75118ea7b18d905a5e7e8ec","tid":432453,"uid":15939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T14:11:43.000Z","msg":"各位巴打, 想請教下呢, 我上網見人玩得好簡單, 腳腳1 TOUCH 好似玩波子機咁彈彈下傳波又大力又準, 我就成日傳錯波, 又細力又唔可以1 TOUCH, 要控一兩下先, 係咪同SETTING有關? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我多數 X 傳完波就會禁L2 拎穩D 先再傳, 有時R1 X 會搞到傳甩波<br />\n<br />\n有冇幾招1ON1 過人既絕技, 用O X假射好似唔多實用, L前R上下搓波行又要迫甩, 應該點先易過到人 (除左傳走)<br />\n<br />\n防守又唔知想點, R1 搵電腦迫又係ON99, 齌陪跑唔會主動搶人波, 手動一個封佢位又要R2 跑, 佢埋埋地身就要L2 咁得佢身位, 即係要R1+R2 , 埋身R1+L2 咁守岩唔岩?定係有其他再有效D 既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家對職業級電腦都只係55波, 求教點樣玩勁D, 設定又有咩一定要SET 可以EFFICIENT D? 唔該"},{"pid":"d79992d7ee323e6ad3b9664ad99d9cc9e2ea9d08","tid":432453,"uid":15939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T14:33:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed10cc5ea84d8f41698007322daeb8aa6128382e","tid":432453,"uid":15939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:12:59.000Z","msg":"再推，連登咁多D1實有大把高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32fb53e10329e9ae552c11b59a2759f1cbb76fa","tid":432453,"uid":36226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:35:36.000Z","msg":"打機都係要練 玩多啲睇多啲<br />\n唔係每個情況都即刻話到你知最好點做<br />\n好多野無得一步登天嫁"},{"pid":"abadcd3c702eddacd5c2d830a90ef14d953f192d","tid":432453,"uid":7715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:38:57.000Z","msg":"唔好跑就ＯＫ"},{"pid":"0ba6759ba30